---
title: Fig Jam and Goat's Cheese Salmon en Croute with Rosemary Roast Potatoes and Pear Salad
description: Serve up a festive feast this winter! Make a meal that's truly special with this lightly indulgent and luxurious Fig Jam and Goat's Cheese Salmon en Croute.
